<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our Store!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4a154b;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a154b;
      color: white !important;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    a {
      color: #4a154b;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="https://example.com/logo.png" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Welcome to Our E-Commerce Store!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining our e-commerce platform. We're excited to have you as a new member of our community!</p>
    <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Shop our exclusive collections</li>
      <li>Track your orders easily</li>
      <li>Save your favorite items</li>
      <li>Get personalized recommendations</li>
      <li>Access special promotions for members</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Ready to start shopping? Click the button below to browse our latest products:</p>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Start Shopping</a>
    </p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to contact our friendly customer support team at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Your E-Commerce Store. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>123 E-Commerce Street, Shopping City, SC 12345</p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://example.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
      <a href="https://example.com/terms">Terms of Service</a> | 
      <a href="https://example.com/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 